      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * Abyss</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Lysefjorden_-_Man_standing_on_Preikestolen.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Lysefjorden_-_Man_standing_on_Preikestolen.JPG/330px-Lysefjorden_-_Man_standing_on_Preikestolen.JPG\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Lysefjorden_-_Man_standing_on_Preikestolen.JPG/500px-Lysefjorden_-_Man_standing_on_Preikestolen.JPG 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Lysefjorden_-_Man_standing_on_Preikestolen.JPG/960px-Lysefjorden_-_Man_standing_on_Preikestolen.JPG 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Lysefjorden_-_Man_standing_on_Preikestolen.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>At the Edge of the Abyss <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Abyss</b>,<br />\na <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Chinese Chess</a> program by <a href=\"/Chun_Ye\" title=\"Chun Ye\">Chun Ye</a> and <a href=\"/Tony_Marsland\" title=\"Tony Marsland\">Tony Marsland</a>, written in <a href=\"/C\" title=\"C\">C</a> under <a href=\"/Unix\" title=\"Unix\">Unix</a> aka <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SunOS\">SunOS</a>. A <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/X_Window_System\">X Window</a> <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> was written in <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Haiying_Wang&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Haiying Wang (page does not exist)\">Haiying Wang</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. The program was subject of Chun Ye's 1992 master thesis at <a href=\"/University_of_Alberta\" title=\"University of Alberta\">University of Alberta</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> on the topic of <a href=\"/Selectivity\" title=\"Selectivity\">selectivity</a> and <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">extension heuristics</a> in the domain of Chinese Chess. Not only Ye's advisor, Tony Marsland, contributed to the development of the program, but also <a href=\"/Don_Beal\" title=\"Don Beal\">Don Beal</a> - at that time visiting professor at University of Alberta - in particular concerning <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning#NMQS\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">null move quiescence search</a>. \n</p><p>Abyss participated at all three <a href=\"/Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"Computer Olympiad\">Computer Olympiads</a> which took place in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maastricht\">Maastricht</a>, winning the gold medal (shared) at the <a href=\"/3rd_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"3rd Computer Olympiad\">3rd Computer Olympiad, 1991</a>, while the 1999 version played in <a href=\"/6th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"6th Computer Olympiad\">2001</a> and <a href=\"/7th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"7th Computer Olympiad\">2002</a>, respectively. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Description\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Description</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Move_Generation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Move Generation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Search\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Search</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-3 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Basics\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Basics</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-3 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Move_Ordering\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Move Ordering</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-3 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Selectivity\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selectivity</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Evaluation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Evaluation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Abyss.27_ICGA_Tournaments\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Abyss' ICGA Tournaments</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-13\"><a href=\"#Engine\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Engine</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-14\"><a href=\"#Misc_2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-15\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Description\">Description</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Abyss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Description\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>The framework of Abyss <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> was based on the Western experimental Chess program <a href=\"/Parabelle\" title=\"Parabelle\">Parabelle</a> by <a href=\"/Fred_Popowich\" title=\"Fred Popowich\">Fred Popowich</a> and Tony Marsland <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Move_Generation\"><a href=\"/Move_Generation\" title=\"Move Generation\">Move Generation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Abyss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Move Generation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Abyss' board is <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess_Board_Representation\" title=\"Chinese Chess Board Representation\">represented</a> as <a href=\"/Mailbox\" title=\"Mailbox\">Mailbox</a> - a one-dimensional <a href=\"/Array\" title=\"Array\">array</a> of 90 computer words, indexed by 0 .. 89. Pieces are encoded by ±1 for red and black pawns until ±7 for red and black kings, empty squares are represented by zero. To detect the edges of the board and <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess#Palace\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">palace</a> during move generation, board arrays of pre-computed 12-bit <a href=\"/Direction\" title=\"Direction\">direction</a> masks consisting of four groups for each orthogonal direction of 3 bits each are utilized. Only the empty intersection of the move direction with the mask of the <a href=\"/Target_Square\" title=\"Target Square\">target square</a> indicates target on board or inside palace, followed by piece specific tests to generate <a href=\"/Pseudo-Legal_Move\" title=\"Pseudo-Legal Move\">pseudo legal moves</a> or to continue a direction loop for rook or <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess#Cannon\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">cannon</a>. Detection of strictly <a href=\"/Legal_Move\" title=\"Legal Move\">legal moves</a>, i.e. it does not expose the own king in check, or does not oppose both kings on the same file with no pieces intervening, is delayed until the move is actually made for efficiency reasons - since not all generated pseudo legal moves are examined.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Search\"><a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Abyss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Search\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The search procedure of Abyss was subject of Chun Ye's thesis concerning <a href=\"/Selectivity\" title=\"Selectivity\">selectivity</a>, in particular <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">extensions</a> which are combined in various experiments, and further elaborated in two additional papers along with Tony Marsland <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>. Abyss already featured <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">recursive null move pruning</a> with <a href=\"/Depth_Reduction_R\" title=\"Depth Reduction R\">depth reduction</a> of 1 <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>, and further <a href=\"/Don_Beal\" title=\"Don Beal\">Don Beal's</a> <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning#NMQS\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">null move quiescence search</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>. A piece evading move extension was motivated by threat detection concerning the complicated <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">repetition</a> rules of Chinese Chess.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Basics\">Basics</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Abyss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Basics\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Iterative Deepening\">Iterative Deepening</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">Aspiration Windows</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a href=\"/Zobrist_Hashing\" title=\"Zobrist Hashing\">Zobrist Hashing</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Refutation_Table\" title=\"Refutation Table\">Refutation Table</a></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Move_Ordering\"><a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Abyss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Move Ordering\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Hash_Move\" title=\"Hash Move\">Hash Move</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Refutation_Move\" title=\"Refutation Move\">Refutation Move</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/MVV-LVA\" title=\"MVV-LVA\">MVV/LVA</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/History_Heuristic\" title=\"History Heuristic\">History Heuristic</a></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selectivity\"><a href=\"/Selectivity\" title=\"Selectivity\">Selectivity</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Abyss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Selectivity\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">Extensions</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a href=\"/Check_Extensions\" title=\"Check Extensions\">Check Evasion Extensions</a></dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/Recapture_Extensions\" title=\"Recapture Extensions\">Recapture Extensions</a></dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/Mate_Threat_Extensions\" title=\"Mate Threat Extensions\">King Threats</a></dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/One_Reply_Extensions\" title=\"One Reply Extensions\">One Reply Extensions</a></dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/Singular_Extensions\" title=\"Singular Extensions\">Singular Extensions</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Pruning\" title=\"Pruning\">Pruning</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Recursive Null Move Pruning</a> with <a href=\"/Depth_Reduction_R\" title=\"Depth Reduction R\">R</a> = 1</dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning#NMQS\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Don Beal's Null Move Quiescence Search</a></dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Futility Pruning</a></dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></dd></dl>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Evaluation\"><a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Abyss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Evaluation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">Material Balance</a> with <a href=\"/Point_Value\" title=\"Point Value\">Point Values</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd><table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\n<tr>\n<th> Piece\n</th>\n<th> Opening\n</th>\n<th> Endgame\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\"> <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess#King\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">King</a>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"2\"> 7000\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">  <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess#Rook\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Rook</a>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"2\"> 1800\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">  <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess#Cannon\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Cannon</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 900\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 800\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">  <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess#Horse\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Horse</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 800\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 900\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">  <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess#Elephant\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Elephant</a>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"2\"> 300\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">  <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess#Advisor\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Advisor</a>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"2\"> 300\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">  <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess#Pawn\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Pawn</a>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"2\"> 100\n</td></tr></table></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Piece-Square_Tables\" title=\"Piece-Square Tables\">Piece-Square Tables</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Square_Control\" title=\"Square Control\">Square Control</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/King_Safety\" title=\"King Safety\">King Safety</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a href=\"/King_Safety#Attacking\" title=\"King Safety\">Attacking King Zone</a></dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/King_Safety#Patterns\" title=\"King Safety\">Penalty for King</a> on <a href=\"/Ranks\" title=\"Ranks\">rank</a> or <a href=\"/Files\" title=\"Files\">file</a> of opponent's <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess#Cannon\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Cannon</a></dd></dl>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Abyss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Abyss.27_ICGA_Tournaments\">Abyss' ICGA Tournaments</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Abyss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: Abyss&#039; ICGA Tournaments\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\">\n\n<tr>\n<th> Edition\n</th>\n<th> Version\n</th>\n<th> Ranking\n</th>\n<th> Participants\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/3rd_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"3rd Computer Olympiad\">3rd Computer Olympiad, Maastricht 1991</a>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 1\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 2\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/6th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"6th Computer Olympiad\">6th Computer Olympiad, Maastricht 2001</a>\n</td>\n<td>  Abyss '99\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 3\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 3\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/7th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"7th Computer Olympiad\">7th Computer Olympiad, Maastricht 2002</a>\n</td>\n<td>  Abyss '99\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 4\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\"> 4\n</td></tr></table>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Abyss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Parabelle\" title=\"Parabelle\">Parabelle</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Abyss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Chun_Ye\" title=\"Chun Ye\">Chun Ye</a> (<b>1992</b>). <i>Experiments in Selective Search Extensions</i>. M.Sc. thesis, Department of Computing Science, <a href=\"/University_of_Alberta\" title=\"University of Alberta\">University of Alberta</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://era.library.ualberta.ca/public/datastream/get/uuid:e4fbf48d-7603-490f-85cc-5497bbecf5a8/DS1\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Chun_Ye\" title=\"Chun Ye\">Chun Ye</a>, <a href=\"/Tony_Marsland\" title=\"Tony Marsland\">Tony Marsland</a> (<b>1992</b>). <i>Experiments in Forward Pruning with Limited Extensions.</i> <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#15_2\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 15, No. 2</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~tony/RecentPapers/Experiments-FP-YeMars-1992.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Chun_Ye\" title=\"Chun Ye\">Chun Ye</a>, <a href=\"/Tony_Marsland\" title=\"Tony Marsland\">Tony Marsland</a> (<b>1992</b>). <i>Selective Extensions in Game-Tree Search.</i> <a href=\"/3rd_Computer_Olympiad#Workshop\" title=\"3rd Computer Olympiad\">Heuristic Programming in AI 3</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~tony/RecentPapers/SelectiveExten-YeMars.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Abyss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Engine\">Engine</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Abyss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13\" title=\"Edit section: Engine\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/program.php?id=252\">Abyss' ICGA Tournaments</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc_2\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Abyss&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/abyss\">abyss - Wiktionary</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abyss\">Abyss from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abyssal_zone\">Abyssal zone from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abyssal_plain\">Abyssal plain from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abyss_(comics)\">Abyss (comics) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abyss_(religion)\">Abyss (religion) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abyss_(roller_coaster)\">Abyss (roller coaster) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abyss_(Thelema)\">Abyss (Thelema) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abyssinia\">Abyssinia from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/In_the_Abyss\">In the Abyss - Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ex